<p>服务端有一个<code v-pre>GetHgService</code>的类，里面有个<code v-pre>getName()</code>方法</p>
<div class="language-typescript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="ts" data-title="ts"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token keyword">export</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">GetHgService</span> <span class="token keyword">implements</span> <span class="token class-name">GetHgServer</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
