<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>由于服务端的getName方法里面调用了一个客户端的方法：<code v-pre>this.client.onDone()</code>，方法体如下：</p>
<div class="language-typescript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="ts" data-title="ts"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token keyword">export</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">HGClient</span> <span class="token keyword">implements</span> <span class="token class-name">GetHgClient</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line">    <span class="token function">onDone</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>args<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token builtin">string</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line">        <span class="token builtin">console</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"client-message:execute onDone!"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span>
<span class="line">        <span class="token builtin">console</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>args <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"done!"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span>
<span class="line">    <span class="token punctuation">}</span></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token punctuation">}</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>因此客户端浏览器里会输出：</p>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="text" data-title="text"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">websocket open!</span>
